dcterms:description: The Google Street View dataset consists of 43,392 building facade images, distributed to 14,512 commercial, 14,184 other, and 14,696 residential buildings. It is used as a seed dataset for finding structurally similar images in the social media dataset and for fine-tuning state-of-the-art CNN architectures on the given task.
dcterms:title: Google Street View Dataset

dcterms:description: The Flickr Social Media Dataset consists of 28,818,438 images collected from 42 cities across the globe using the Flickr API. The dataset is filtered to yield high-quality, geo-tagged images for building function classification.
dcterms:title: Flickr Social Media Dataset
